<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">أَبِي وَائِلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>-<span class="c5"> <span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا يَنْبَغِي لِأَحَدٍ أَنْ يَكُونَ خَيْرًا مِنِ ابْنِ مَتَّى.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>